uage=en|publisher=Soccerway|date=2012-09-19|archive-date=2020-08-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200808234429/https://uk.soccerway.com/matches/2012/09/19/europe/uefa-champions-league/joint-stock-company-fc-shakhtar-donetsk/fc-nordsjalland/1388722/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，賽後他被選為全場最佳球員和入選本輪最佳球員<ref>{{cite web| title = Mkhitaryan named the Man of the Match| url = http://shakhtar.com/en/news/23533| accessdate = 2013-07-21| language = en| date = 2012-09-20| publisher = Shakhtar Donetsk| archive-date = 2016-08-05| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160805104834/http://shakhtar.com/en/news/23533| dead-url = no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web| title = Mkhitaryan named in the Team of the Week| url = http://shakhtar.com/en/news/23573| date = 2012-09-21| language = en| accessdate = 2013-07-21| publisher = Shakhtar Donetsk| archive-date = 2016-08-05| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160805105907/http://shakhtar.com/en/news/23573| dead-url = no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|script-title=uk:Чемпіонат ПЛ|url=http://www.fpl.ua/ukr/fans/liga/|publisher=fpl.ua|accessdate=2013-03-04|language=Uk|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100729145528/http://www.fpl.ua/ukr/fans/liga/|archivedate=2010-07-29}}</ref>。2013年3月16日，米希達恩在對陣祖奴摩勒斯有份上陣，第100次為球隊於聯賽上陣<ref>{{cite web|script-title=hy:Հենրիխ Մխիթարյանը 100-րդ խաղն է անցկացնում Ուկրաինայի առաջնությունում|url=http://sport.news.am/arm/news/20705/henrikh-mkhitaryany-100-rd-khaxn-e-anckacnum-ukrainayi-arajnutyunum.html|publisher=sport.news.am|accessdate=2013-03-17|language=hy|date=2013-03-16|archive-date=2020-02-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200217161655/https://sport.news.am/arm/news/20705/henrikh-mkhitaryany-100-rd-khaxn-e-anckacnum-ukrainayi-arajnutyunum.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|script-title= hy:Հենրիխ Մխիթարյանի հերթական գոլը|url= http://sport.news.am/arm/news/20706/henrikh-mkhitaryani-hertakan-goly.html|publisher= sport.news.am|accessdate= 2013-03-17|language= hy|date= 2013-03-16|archive-date= 2020-08-05|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20200805171741/https://sport.news.am/arm/news/20706/henrikh-mkhitaryani-hertakan-goly.html|dead-url= no}}</ref>。

