=== 多蒙特 ===
==== 2013-14賽季 ====
2013年6月25日，多蒙特出價2,500萬英鎊（3,000萬歐元），希望買下米希達恩<ref>{{cite news|last=Drayton|first=John|title=Shakhtar open to Mkhitaryan offers as Anzhi join Liverpool and Dortmund in £25m chase|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/sport/football/article-2350019/Shakhtar-open-Henrikh-Mkhitaryan-offers-Anzhi-join-Liverpool-Dortmund-25m-chase.html|accessdate=2013-06-27|language=en|newspaper=Daily Mirror|date=2013-06-27|archive-date=2020-08-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200807210025/https://www.dailymail.co.uk/sport/football/article-2350019/Shakhtar-open-Henrikh-Mkhitaryan-offers-Anzhi-join-Liverpool-Dortmund-25m-chase.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last=Lee|first=Sam|title=Borussia Dortmund launch €23 million bid for Mkhitaryan|url=http://www.goal.com/en-ng/news/4102/transfer-zone/2013/06/26/4075934/borussia-dortmund-launch-23-million-bid-for-mkhitaryan|accessdate=2013-06-27|language=en|publisher=Goal.com|date=2013-06-26|archive-date=2020-09-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200922072459/https://www.goal.com/en-ng/news/4102/transfer-zone/2013/06/26/4075934/borussia-dortmund-launch-23-million-bid-for-mkhitaryan|dead-url=no}}</ref>，但薩克達球隊總監謝爾蓋·柏爾堅（Sergei Palkin）認為多蒙特出價過低，球會認為多蒙特應出價3,000萬英鎊（3,600萬歐元）。同一场新闻发布会上，柏爾堅亦確認於[[國際體育會|-{zh-hans:国际体育俱乐部; zh-hant:國際體育會;}-]]簽下[[費特·洛迪古斯|-{zh-cn:弗雷德里科·罗德里格斯·桑托斯;zh-hk:費特·洛迪古斯;zh-tw:佛雷德里科·羅德里奎斯·桑托斯;}-]]，轉會費為1,250萬英鎊（1,500萬歐元），媒体推测这是为了顶替即将离队的米希達恩<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www1.skysports.com/football/news/11669/8794018/Transfer-news-Borussia-Dortmund-have-bid-for-Henrikh-Mkhitaryan|title=Borussia Dortmund have bid for Henrikh Mkhitaryan|publisher=Sky Sports|date=2013-06-26|accessdate=2013-06-26|language=en|archive-date=2020-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112031759/https://www.skysports.com/football/news/11669/8794018/Transfer-news-Borussia-Dortmund-have-bid-for-Henrikh-Mkhitaryan|dead-url=no}}</ref>。7月5日，有報導指多蒙特成功收購他，球員正前往德國進行體檢<ref>{{cite news|last=Edwards|first=John|title=Dortmund beat Liverpool and Spurs to £20m-rated playmaker Mkhitaryan|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/sport/football/article-2356872/Borussia-Dortmund-beat-Liverpool-Henrikh-Mkhitaryan.html?ico=sport%5Eheadlines|accessdate=2013-07-05|language=en|newspaper=Daily Mail|date=2013-07-05|archive-date=2020-08-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200809054123/https://www.dailymail.co.uk/sport/football/article-2356872/Borussia-Dortmund-beat-Liverpool-Henrikh-Mkhitaryan.html?ico=sport%5Eheadlines|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last= McNulty|first= Phil|title= Henrikh Mkhitaryan: Liverpool target set for Borussia Dortmund|url= http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/23207884|accessdate= 2013-07-06|language= en|date= 2013-07-05|agency= BBC Sport|archive-date= 2013-10-23|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20131023062923/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/23207884|dead-url= no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last=Anderson|first=David|title=Liverpool set to miss out on Henrikh Mkhitaryan who is Borussia Dortmund bound after Shakhtar Donetsk accept £21.5m bid|url=http://www.mirror.co.uk/sport/football/transfer-news/liverpool-transfers-henrikh-mkhitaryan-looks-2030353|accessdate=2013-07-06|language=en|newspaper=Daily Mirror|date=2013-07-06|archive-date=2020-10-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201024070831/https://www.mirror.co.uk/sport/football/transfer-news/liverpool-transfers-henrikh-mkhitaryan-looks-2030353|dead-url=no}}</ref>。8日，多蒙特官方宣佈米希達恩將轉會，簽約4年，轉會費為約2,150萬英鎊（2,500萬歐元）<ref>{{cite news|last=Christenson|first=Marcus|title=Liverpool set to miss out on No1 summer target Henrikh Mkhitaryan|url=https://www.theguardian.com/football/2013/jul/05/henrikh-mkhitaryan-dortmund-liverpool-transfer|accessdate=2013-07-08|language=en|newspaper=The Guardian|date=2013-07-05|archive-date=2020-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112030237/http://www.theguardian.com/football/2013/jul/05/henrikh-mkhitaryan-dortmund-liverpool-transfer|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title= Dortmund win race for Shakhtar's Mkhitaryan|url= http://www.uefa.com/uefachampionsleague/news/newsid=1969552.html|accessdate= 2013-07-08|language= en|newspaper= uefa.com|date= 2013-07-08|archive-date= 2019-12-06|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20191206082130/https://www.uefa.com/uefachampionsleague/news/newsid=1969552.html|dead-url= no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last=Turnbull|first=Craig|title=Dortmund confirm Mkhitaryan transfer|url=http://www.goal.com/en/news/11/transfer-zone/2013/07/08/4103038/breaking-news-dortmund-confirm-mkhitaryan-deal|accessdate=2013-07-08|language=en|newspaper=Goal.com|date=2013-07-08|archive-date=2020-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112013722/https://www.goal.com/en/news/11/transfer-zone/2013/07/08/4103038/breaking-news-dortmund-confirm-mkhitaryan-deal|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Dortmund expected to tie up 'difficult' Mkhitaryan deal|url= http://www.espn.co.uk/football/sport/story/219785.html|accessdate= 2013-07-08|date= 2013-07-08|agency=ESPN}}</ref>。薩克達和多蒙特完成「所有必需的正式手續」後，費用為2,360萬英鎊（2,750萬歐元）<ref>{{cite news|title= Henrikh Mkhitaryan disappoints Liverpool by joining Borussia|url= https://www.theguardian.com/football/2013/jul/09/henrikh-mkhitaryan-joins-borussia-dortmund|accessdate= 2013-07-10|newspaper= The Guardian|language= en|date= 2013-07-09|archive-date= 2017-02-27|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20170227063107/https://www.theguardian.com/football/2013/jul/09/henrikh-mkhitaryan-joins-borussia-dortmund|dead-url= no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title= Shakhtar parted with Mkhitaryan|url= http://shakhtar.com/en/news/27453|accessdate= 2013-07-08|date= 2013-07-09|language= en|agency= FC Shakhtar Donetsk|archive-date= 2016-09-13|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20160913130708/http://shakhtar.com/en/news/27453|dead-url= no}}</ref>，成為多蒙特歷史上最昂貴的收購球員<ref>{{cite news|title= Henrikh Mkhitaryan's transfer – most expensive in Borussia's history|url= http://armenpress.am/eng/news/725381/henrikh-mkhitaryan%E2%80%99s-transfer-%E2%80%93-most-expensive-in-borussia%E2%80%99s-history.html|accessdate= 2013-07-10|language= en|newspaper= Armenpress|date= 2013-07-09|archive-date= 2013-07-11|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20130711123928/http://armenpress.am/eng/news/725381/henrikh-mkhitaryan%E2%80%99s-transfer-%E2%80%93-most-expensive-in-borussia%E2%80%99s-history.html|dead-url= no}}</ref>。

