tml|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在對陣[[法兰克福足球俱乐部|法兰克福]]的比賽中，米希達恩梅開二度，帶領球隊以2比1勝出，繼續排列聯賽榜首<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.bvb.de/?k%E5%85%ECY%1B%E7%F4%9C%5Co%E3%8D%99 | title = 2–1: Mkhitaryan seals fourth BVB win with two goals | publisher = Borussia Dortmund | date = 2013-09-01 | accessdate = 2013-09-08 | language = en | archive-date = 2020-09-21 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200921171113/https://www.bvb.de/?k%E5%85%ECY%1B%E7%F4%9C%5Co%E3%8D%99 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。於客勝[[阿仙奴足球會|阿仙奴]]2比1的比賽中，他攻入轉會後首個歐洲聯賽冠軍盃入球。

本賽季，米希達恩於德甲聯賽攻入9球，交出10次助攻，被列入WhoScored德甲最佳陣容，多蒙特最終以次名完成聯賽，德國盃亦屈居亞軍<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.sports.ru/football/1020710220.html | script-title = ru:Мхитарян попал в символическую сборную чемпионата Германии по версии официального сайта Бундеслиги | language = ru | publisher = sports.ru | date = 2014-05-20 | accessdate = 2014-05-21 | archive-date = 2020-09-22 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200922071742/https://www.sports.ru/football/1020710220.html | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="whoscored.com">{{cite web | url = http://www.whoscored.com/Articles/78ylhxlirkgaac1jq3vd-g/Show/League-Focus-Bundesliga-201314-Season-Review | title = League Focus: Bundesliga 2013/14 Season Review | publisher = whoscored.com | date = 2014-05-12 | accessdate = 2014-05-21 | first = Andy | last = Brassell | language = en | archive-date = 2020-09-25 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200925184811/https://www.whoscored.com/Articles/78ylhxlirkgaac1jq3vd-g/Show/League-Focus-Bundesliga-201314-Season-Review | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

==== 2014-15賽季 ====
米希達恩於{{link-en|2014年德國超級盃|2014 DFL-Supercup}}對陣[[拜仁慕尼黑足球會|拜仁慕尼黑]]的比賽中攻入1球，協助球隊以2比0擊敗對手奪冠<ref>{{cite web|url= https://www.theguardian.com/football/2014/aug/13/borussia-dortmund-bayern-munich-german-supercup-match-report|title= Borussia Dortmund beat Bayern Munich to win German Supercup again|date= 2014-08-13|language= en|work= Guardian|accessdate= 2014-11-20|archive-date= 2019-04-02|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20190402082156/https://www.theguardian.com/football/2014/aug/13/borussia-dortmund-bayern-munich-german-supercup-match-report|dead-url= no}}</ref>。2014年9月，他因受傷而需避戰一個月<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.sports.ru/football/1023754768.html | title = Мхитарян выбыл на месяц из-за травмы голеностопа | language = ru | publisher = sports.ru | date = 2014-09-21 | accessdate = 2014-12-16 | archive-date = 2020-09-22 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200922074907/https://www.sports.ru/football/1023754768.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>；12月13日，他再次受傷<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.sports.ru/football/1025721964.htm | title = Мхитарян не выйдет на поле до конца 2014 года | language = ru | publisher = sports.ru | date = 2014-12-24 | accessdate = 2014-12-26 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141226130516/http://www.sports.ru/football/1025721964.htm | archivedate = 2014-12-26 }}</ref>。2015年2月28日，他在[[魯爾區德比|魯爾區德比]]對陣[[沙尔克04足球俱乐部|沙尔克04]]的比賽中取得入球，協助球隊大勝3比0<ref>{{cite news|title= Borussia Dortmund continue revival with three-goal spree to beat Schalke|url= https://www.theguardian.com/football/2015/feb/28/borussia-dortmund-schalke-bundesliga-match-report|accessdate= 2015-08-20|work= The Guardian|publisher= Reuters|date= 2015-02-28|language= en|archive-date= 2020-11-10|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20201110123222/https://www.theguardian.com/football/2015/feb/28/borussia-dortmund-schalke-bundesliga-match-report|dead-url= no}}</ref>。

==== 2015-16賽季 ====
2015年8月6日，多蒙特在歐足協歐霸盃外圍賽第三圈次回合的比賽中，於主場迎戰奧地利的[[禾夫斯貝加體育會|禾夫斯貝加]]，教練[[托马斯·图赫尔|-{zh-hans:托马斯·图赫尔; zh-hk:湯瑪士·杜曹; zh-tw:托馬斯·圖赫爾}-]]首次於主場領軍，米希達恩在比賽末段完成帽子戲法，球隊最終在次回合以5比0勝出，兩回合計以6比0勝出並晉級附加賽<ref>{{cite news|title= Borussia Dortmund 5 Wolfsberger 0 (6–0 agg): Mkhitaryan lights up Tuchel home bow|url= http://www.fourfourtwo.com/news/borussia-dortmund-5-wolfsberger-0-6-0-agg-mkhitaryan-lights-tuchel-home-bow|accessdate= 2015-08-07|work= FourFourTwo|date= 2015-08-06|language= en|archive-date= 2020-08-07|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20200807220117/https://www.fourfourtwo.com/news/borussia-dortmund-5-wolfsberger-0-6-0-agg-mkhitaryan-lights-tuchel-home-bow|dead-url= no}}</ref>。3日後，他在德國盃首圈對陣[[开姆尼茨足球俱乐部|真尼沙]]的比賽中攻入1球，協助球隊以2比0勝出<ref>{{cite news|title=Chemnitzer 0–2 Borussia Dortmund: Aubameyang & Mkhitaryan see BVB through|url=http://www.goal.com/en/match/chemnitzer-fc-vs-borussia-dortmund/2038928/report|accessdate=2015-08-14|language=en|publisher=Goal.com|date=2015-08-09|archive-date=2016-07-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160723082750/http://www.goal.com/en/match/chemnitzer-fc-vs-borussia-dortmund/2038928/report|dead-url=no}}</ref>。8月15日，米希達恩在聯賽首戰對陣[[门兴格拉德巴赫足球俱乐部|慕遜加柏]]的比賽中梅開二度，協助球隊以4比0勝出<ref>{{cite news|title= Bor Dortmd 4–0 Borussia Monchengladbach|url= http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/33541336|accessdate= 2015-08-15|language= en|publisher= BBC Sport|date= 2015-08-15|archive-date= 2015-10-03|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20151003005402/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/33541336|dead-url= no}}</ref>。5日後，他在歐足協歐霸盃附加賽對陣[[奧特足球會|奧特]]的首回合比賽中，以頭鎚攻入1球，助球隊以4比3反勝對手<ref>{{cite news|title=Odd 3 Dortmund 4: Mkhitaryan seals remarkable comeback|url=http://www.fourfourtwo.com/news/odd-3-dortmund-4-mkhitaryan-seals-remarkable-comeback|accessdate=2015-08-20|language=en|work=FourFourTwo|date=2015-08-20|archive-date=2015-09-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924044714/http://www.fourfourtwo.com/news/odd-3-dortmund-4-mkhitaryan-seals-remarkable-comeback|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2015年10月28日，米希達恩在本土盃賽第二圈的比賽中攻入1球，助球隊以7比1大勝[[柏達邦07體育會|-{zh-cn:帕德博恩07; zh-hk:柏達邦; zh-tw:帕德博恩;}-]]晉級<ref>{{cite news|title=Bor Dortmd 7–1 SC Paderborn 07|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/34621132|accessdate=2015-10-28|language=en|publisher=BBC Sport|date=2015-10-28|archive-date=2015-11-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151101145342/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/34621132|dead-url=no}}</ref>。8日後，他於歐足協歐霸盃小組賽最後一輪對陣[[卡巴拉足球會|卡巴拉]]的比賽中，攻入1球，助球隊以4比0勝出，取得三十二強的席位<ref>{{cite news|last1=Buczko|first1=Stefan|title=Henrikh Mkhitaryan stars for Borussia Dortmund in Europa League win|url=http://www.espnfc.co.uk/club/borussia-dortmund/124/blog/post/2700706/henrikh-mkhitaryan-stars-for-borussia-dortmund-in-europa|accessdate=2015-11-08|publisher=ESPN|date=2015-11-06|language=en|archive-date=2019-09-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190910200034/http://www.espnfc.co.uk/club/borussia-dortmund/124/blog/post/2700706/henrikh-mkhitaryan-stars-for-borussia-dortmund-in-europa|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2016年4月20日，米希達恩於德國盃準決賽中攻入1球，最終球隊以3比1戰勝[[柏林赫塔體育俱樂部|哈化柏林]]，晉級決賽<ref>{{cite news|url= http://www.dw.com/en/marco-reus-drives-borussia-dortmund-past-hertha-berlin-to-german-cup-final/a-19201920|title= Marco Reus drives Borussia Dortmund past Hertha Berlin to German Cup final|date= 2016-04-20|language= en|work= Deutsche Welle|access-date= 2016-04-21|archive-date= 2020-08-09|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20200809011717/https://www.dw.com/en/marco-reus-drives-borussia-dortmund-past-hertha-berlin-to-german-cup-final/a-19201920|dead-url= no}}</ref>。賽季完結後，他當選了[[踢球者|踢球者]]德甲最佳球員<ref name="asbarez.com">{{cite web | url = http://asbarez.com/150847/henrikh-mkhitaryan-voted-bundesligas-player-of-the-season/ | title = Henrikh Mkhitaryan Voted Bundesliga’s Player of the Season | date = 2016-05-25 | language = en | website = asbarez.com | access-date = 2016-05-30 | archive-date = 2020-08-17 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200817115924/http://asbarez.com/150847/henrikh-mkhitaryan-voted-bundesligas-player-of-the-season/ | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="news.am">{{cite web | url = http://sport.news.am/eng/news/67769/mkhitaryan-truly-honored-to-be-voted-best-player-of-the-season!.html | title = Mkhitaryan: Truly honored to be voted Best Player of the Season! | website = sport.news.am | date = 2016-05-25 | language = en | access-date = 2016-05-30 | archive-date = 2020-08-08 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200808011525/https://sport.news.am/eng/news/67769/mkhitaryan-truly-honored-to-be-voted-best-player-of-the-season!.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>，並以15個聯賽助攻成為當季德甲助攻王<ref name="auto">{{cite web | url = http://www.foxsports.com/soccer/stats?competition=4&season=2015&category=STANDARD&pos=0&team=0&isOpp=0&splitType=0&sort=6&sortOrder=0 | title = 2015–16 Bundesliga Player Standard Stats by Assists | website = FOX Soccer | access-date = 2016-05-30 | language = en | archive-date = 2019-10-28 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20191028212945/https://www.foxsports.com/soccer/stats?competition=4&season=2015&category=STANDARD&pos=0&team=0&isOpp=0&splitType=0&sort=6&sortOrder=0 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="worldfootball.net">{{cite web | url = http://www.worldfootball.net/assists/bundesliga-2015-2016/ | title = Bundesliga 2015/2016 – Assists | website = worldfootball.net | access-date = 2016-05-30 | language = en | archive-date = 2020-12-25 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201225163544/https://www.worldfootball.net/assists/bundesliga-2015-2016/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

=== 曼聯 ===
==== 2016-17賽季 ====
[[File:Mkhitaryan_144856.jpg|thumb]]

2016年7月2日，多蒙特的行政總監{{link-en|汉斯-约阿希姆·瓦茨克|Hans-Joachim Watzke|-{zh-hant:漢斯·祖亞金·華斯基;zh-hans:汉斯-约阿希姆·瓦茨克}-}}表示，售賣米希達恩至曼聯是無可避免，因為球員與球會只剩下一年合約，若不售賣，球員於半年後將能免費轉會<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/36693832|title=Henrikh Mkhitaryan: Man Utd sign forward, say Borussia Dortmund|publisher=BBC Sport|date=2016-07-02|accessdate=2016-07-02|language=en|archive-date=2021-01-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210113024720/https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/36693832|dead-url=no}}</ref>。4日後，他以2,700萬至3,000萬英鎊的價錢轉會至[[英格蘭超級足球聯賽|英格蘭超級足球聯賽]]球會[[曼徹斯特聯足球會|曼聯]]，簽約4年<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.theguardian.com/football/2016/jul/06/manchester-united-henrikh-mkhitaryan-signs|title=Manchester United complete signing of Henrikh Mkhitaryan on four-year deal|newspaper=The Guardian|date=2016-07-06|accessdate=2016-08-10|language=en|archive-date=2020-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112004723/https://www.theguardian.com/football/2016/jul/06/manchester-united-henrikh-mkhitaryan-signs|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.mirror.co.uk/sport/football/news/manchester-united-new-boy-henrikh-8455588|title=Manchester United new boy Henrikh Mkhitaryan sets sights on title success|work=Daily Mirror|last=Burrows|first=Ben|date=2016-07-20|language=en|accessdate=2016-08-09|archive-date=2020-09-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200922155609/https://www.mirror.co.uk/sport/football/news/manchester-united-new-boy-henrikh-8455588|dead-url=no}}</ref>，球會有權延長合約年期1年<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.manutd.com/en/News-And-Features/Football-News/2016/Jul/Manchester-United-confirms-signing-of-Henrikh-Mkhitaryan-from-Borussia-Dortmund.aspx|title=United sign Henrikh Mkhitaryan|website=ManUtd.com|publisher=Manchester United|date=2016-07-06|language=en|accessdate=2016-07-06|archive-date=2018-05-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180530040000/http://www.manutd.com/en/News-And-Features/Football-News/2016/Jul/Manchester-United-confirms-signing-of-Henrikh-Mkhitaryan-from-Borussia-Dortmund.aspx|dead-url=no}}</ref>。米希達恩成為首位加盟英超球會的亞美尼亞人<ref>{{cite news|last1=Kearns|first1=Sean|title=Henrikh Mkhitaryan set to become first Armenian to play in the Premier League after joining Manchester United|url=http://metro.co.uk/2016/07/06/henrikh-mkhitaryan-set-to-become-first-armenian-to-play-in-the-premier-league-after-joining-manchester-united-5990619/|accessdate=2016-12-26|work=Metro|date=2016-07-06|language=en|archive-date=2020-08-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200814150538/https://metro.co.uk/2016/07/06/henrikh-mkhitaryan-set-to-become-first-armenian-to-play-in-the-premier-league-after-joining-manchester-united-5990619/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2016年7月15日，米希達恩於對陣[[韋根足球會|韋根]]的友誼賽中首次上陣，球隊最終小勝2比0<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.theguardian.com/football/2016/jul/16/manchester-united-beat-wigan-jose-mourinho-first-game-luke-shaw|title=Manchester United beat Wigan 2–0 in José Mourinho’s first game in charge|work=The Guardian|date=2016-07-16|language=en|accessdate=2016-07-16|archive-date=2020-11-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201110123358/https://www.theguardian.com/football/2016/jul/16/manchester-united-beat-wigan-jose-mourinho-first-game-luke-shaw|dead-url=no}}</ref>。8月7日，他首次於正式比賽上陣，米希達恩於[[英格蘭社區盾|英格蘭社區盾]]對陣[[李斯特城足球會|李斯特城]]時，於補時階段後備入替，最終球隊以2比1擊敗對手奪得社區盾<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bbc.com/sport/football/36934956|title=Leicester City 1–2 Manchester United|publisher=BBC Sport|date=2016-08-07|accessdate=2016-08-24|language=en|archive-date=2021-02-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210201171430/https://www.bbc.com/sport/football/36934956|dead-url=no}}</ref>。8月14日，他在客勝[[般尼茅夫足球會|般尼茅夫]]3比1的比賽中上陣，於第75分鐘後備入替[[桑·馬達|-{zh-hans:胡安·马塔;zh-hk:桑·馬達;zh-tw:胡安·馬塔;}-]]，成為首位於英超上陣的亞美尼亞球員<ref>{{cite news|last1=Ghazanchyan|first1=Siranush|title=Henrikh Mkhitaryan: Honored to be the first Armenian in the Premier League – Video|url=https://www.armradio.am/en/2016/07/06/henrikh-mkhitaryan-honored-to-be-the-first-armenian-in-the-premier-league-video/|accessdate=2016-07-06|language=en|publisher=Public Radio of Armenia|date=2016-07-06|archive-date=2017-09-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170918020954/https://www.armradio.am/en/2016/07/06/henrikh-mkhitaryan-honored-to-be-the-first-armenian-in-the-premier-league-video/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.tribalfootball.com/articles/man-utd-signing-mkhitaryan-first-armenian-and-112th-nationality-in-premier-league-4142382|title=Man Utd signing Mkhitaryan first Armenian and 112th nationality in Premier League|publisher=Tribal Football|date=2016-08-15|accessdate=2016-08-24|language=en|archive-date=2020-09-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200926021032/https://www.tribalfootball.com/articles/man-utd-signing-mkhitaryan-first-armenian-and-112th-nationality-in-premier-league-4142382|dead-url=no}}</ref>。9月10日，米希達恩於[[曼徹斯特德比|曼徹斯特德比]]首次正選上陣，但於半場被被換下<ref>{{cite web | url = https://www.theguardian.com/football/2016/sep/10/jose-mourinho-claudio-bravo-red-rooney-tackle-penalty | title = José Mourinho criticises players and Mark Clattenburg after derby loss | website = The Guardian | date = 2016-09-11 | access-date = 2016-09-11 | language = en | first = Daniel | last = Taylor | archive-date = 2020-11-10 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201110123419/https://www.theguardian.com/football/2016/sep/10/jose-mourinho-claudio-bravo-red-rooney-tackle-penalty | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

2016年12月8日，米希達恩在歐足協歐霸盃對陣[[盧甘斯克索爾亞足球俱樂部|索爾亞]]的比賽中攻入轉會後首球，助球隊作客以2比0取得勝利<ref>{{cite web|url= http://www.uefa.com/uefaeuropaleague/season=2017/matches/round=2000792/match=2019499/index.html|title= Zorya Luhansk vs Manchester United|website= uefa.com|access-date= 2016-12-09|language= en|archive-date= 2019-12-06|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20191206130710/https://www.uefa.com/uefaeuropaleague/season=2017/matches/round=2000792/match=2019499/index.html|dead-url= no}}</ref>。3日後，他在聯賽對陣[[托定咸熱刺足球會|托定咸熱刺]]的比賽射入全場唯一的入球，此球是他英超和在主場攻入的首球，但他於下半場時被對方後衛[[丹尼·路斯|-{zh-hans:丹尼·罗斯;zh-hk:丹尼·路斯;zh-tw:丹尼·羅斯;}-]]踢中腳踝受傷，被換離場<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.manutd.com/en/Fixtures-And-Results/Match-Reports/2016/Dec/Match-Report-Manchester-United-1-Tottenham-Hotspur-0-Premier-League.aspx|website=manutd.com|title=Manchester United vs Tottenham Hotspur 1–0|access-date=2016-12-11|language=en|archive-date=2018-05-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180512080126/http://www.manutd.com/en/Fixtures-And-Results/Match-Reports/2016/Dec/Match-Report-Manchester-United-1-Tottenham-Hotspur-0-Premier-League.aspx|dead-url=no}}</ref>。避戰2場比賽後，米希達恩於對陣[[新特蘭足球會|新特蘭]]的聯賽中復出，並以「蠍子腳」攻入1球，他形容此球為「他所有的入球中最漂亮的一球」<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.manutd.com/en/News-And-Features/Football-News/2016/Dec/player-reaction-henrikh-mkhitaryan-describes-brilliant-strike-v-sunderland-as-his-best-ever-goal.aspx | website = manutd.com | title = Mkhitaryan: It's My Best Goal Ever | date = 2016-12-27 | access-date = 2016-12-27 | first = Mark | last = Froggatt | language = en | archive-date = 2017-09-18 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170918020836/http://www.manutd.com/en/News-And-Features/Football-News/2016/Dec/player-reaction-henrikh-mkhitaryan-describes-brilliant-strike-v-sunderland-as-his-best-ever-goal.aspx | dead-url = no }}</ref>。他於[[2017年歐霸盃決賽|歐足協歐霸盃決賽]]取得入球，助球隊以2比0擊敗[[阿積士足球會|阿積士]]奪冠<ref>{{cite web| url= http://www.manutd.com/en/News-And-Features/Football-News/2017/May/Manchester-United-win-the-Europa-League-after-beating-Ajax-in-the-final-in-Stockholm-24-May-2017.aspx| website= manutd.com| title= United are Europa League Winners| date= 2017-05-25| access-date= 2017-05-25| language= en| first= Adam| last= Higgins| archive-date= 2018-06-01| archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20180601015225/http://www.manutd.com/en/News-And-Features/Football-News/2017/May/Manchester-United-win-the-Europa-League-after-beating-Ajax-in-the-final-in-Stockholm-24-May-2017.aspx| dead-url= no}}</ref>，米希達恩亦成為首位贏得歐洲賽事錦標的亞美尼亞球員<ref name="nytimes2017">{{cite news|last1= Smith|first1= Rory|title= Manchester United’s Henrikh Mkhitaryan Brings Armenia With Him|url= https://www.nytimes.com/2017/05/24/sports/soccer/henrikh-mkhitaryan-armenia.html?_r=0|work= The New York Times|date= 2017-05-24|language= en|accessdate= 2018-01-22|archive-date= 2020-11-10|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20201110123454/https://www.nytimes.com/2017/05/24/sports/soccer/henrikh-mkhitaryan-armenia.html?_r=0|dead-url= no}}</ref>。

