2018年1月22日，[[阿仙奴足球會|阿仙奴]]官方宣佈，米希達恩轉投阿仙奴而[[阿莱克西斯·桑切斯|桑切斯]]則轉投曼聯，兩名球員以互換東家的形式轉會<ref>{{cite web|url= https://www.arsenal.com/news/henrikh-mkhitaryan-signs-alexis-leaves-club|title= Henrikh Mkhitaryan signs as Alexis leaves club|date= 2018-01-23|accessdate= 2018-01-23|language= en|archive-date= 2018-01-24|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20180124025606/https://www.arsenal.com/news/henrikh-mkhitaryan-signs-alexis-leaves-club|dead-url= no}}</ref>。2月3日，米希達恩於主勝[[愛華頓足球會|愛華頓]]5比1的比賽中首次正選上陣，交出3次助攻<ref>{{cite news|title=Arsenal 5-1 Everton|url=http://www.bbc.com/sport/football/42842344|publisher=BBC Sport|date=2018-02-03|language=en|accessdate=2018-02-04|archive-date=2020-11-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201109034610/https://www.bbc.com/sport/football/42842344|dead-url=no}}</ref>。3月8日，米希達恩於[[欧足联欧洲联赛|欧足联欧洲联赛]]對陣[[AC米蘭|AC米蘭]]的比賽中攻入轉會後首個入球，助球隊於十六強首回合客勝2比0<ref>{{cite web|url= http://www.bbc.com/sport/football/43321163|title= AC Milan 0 - 2 Arsenal|language= en|work= BBC|date= 2018-03-08|accessdate= 2018-03-11|archive-date= 2020-11-04|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20201104203003/https://www.bbc.com/sport/football/43321163|dead-url= no}}</ref>。3月11日，他於對陣[[屈福特足球會|屈福特]]的比賽中，射入首個聯賽入球，最終球隊於主場以3比0大勝對手<ref>{{cite web|url= http://www.bbc.com/sport/football/43275529|title= Arsenal 3 - 0 Watford|date= 2018-03-11|accessdate= 2018-03-11|language= en|work= BBC|archive-date= 2020-11-04|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20201104202953/https://www.bbc.com/sport/football/43275529|dead-url= no}}</ref>。4月29日，米希達恩於倒戈對陣[[曼聯|曼聯]]的聯賽中射入1球，入球後，米希達恩出於尊重拒絕慶祝，阿仙奴最終作客以2比1落敗<ref>{{cite news|title= Mavropanos makes his debut: Man Utd V Arsenal teams|url= https://news.arseblog.com/2018/04/mavropanos-makes-his-debut-man-utd-v-arsenal-teams/|accessdate= 2018-04-29|date= 2018-04-29|language= en|archive-date= 2020-11-10|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20201110123531/https://news.arseblog.com/2018/04/mavropanos-makes-his-debut-man-utd-v-arsenal-teams/|dead-url= no}}</ref>。

